

=== edit_stats ===
<b> Edit Stats </b> #CLEAR
+ [Survival = {stat_survival_bonus}]
    -> edit_survival -> edit_stats
+ [Back] -> main_menu
- ->->


=== edit_survival ===
Survival = {stat_survival_bonus}

+ [Add 1]
    ~ stat_survival_bonus++
+ [Subtract 1]
    ~ stat_survival_bonus--
+ [Add 5]
    ~ stat_survival_bonus += 5
+ [Subtract 5]
    ~ stat_survival_bonus -= 5
+ [Back] ->->

- -> edit_survival ->->


